## Input

```css
.mismatched-paren {
  --value: (foo];
  color: red;
}

.mismatched-bracket {
  --value: [foo);
  color: red;
}

.mismatched-brace {
  --value: {foo];
  color: red;
}

.mismatched-before-raw-delimiter {
  --value: (foo] `bar`;
  color: red;
}

.unclosed-paren {
  --value: (foo
}

.unclosed-interpolation {
  --value: #{$gap;
  color: red;
}

.after-recovery {
  color: green;
}

